<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 06:17:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国银行周一维持中期贷款利率不变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-cbank-seen-holding-medium-term-lending-rate-steady-monday-2024-07-12/</link><description>路透调查显示，人们普遍预计中国央行周一将到期贷款展期时将维持中期利率不变，并从银行体系中抽走部分现金。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 06:01:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-cbank-seen-holding-medium-term-lending-rate-steady-monday-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>瓦努阿图总理要求中国银行在维拉港开设分行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vanuatu-prime-minister-asks-bank-china-open-branch-port-villa-2024-07-12/</link><description>瓦努阿图总理夏洛特·萨尔瓦伊办公室周五在一份声明中表示，已要求中国银行在这个太平洋岛国开展业务。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 04:50:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vanuatu-prime-minister-asks-bank-china-open-branch-port-villa-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>即时观点：中国6月原油、未锻轧铜进口量同比下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/view-chinas-june-imports-drop-prospect-seasonal-demand-slowdown-2024-07-12/</link><description>周五海关数据显示，中国6月份大豆、煤炭和铁矿石进口量同比增加，而原油、未锻轧铜和稀土进口量下降。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 04:09:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/view-chinas-june-imports-drop-prospect-seasonal-demand-slowdown-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国出口高于预期，但进口下降意味着更多刺激措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-exports-rise-falling-imports-dampen-june-trade-data-2024-07-12/</link><description>6月份，中国的出口增速创15个月以来最快，这表明制造商在越来越多的贸易伙伴预期征收关税之前提前加载订单，而由于国内需求疲软，进口意外萎缩。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 03:49:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-exports-rise-falling-imports-dampen-june-trade-data-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国斥责欧盟就南海问题发表声明</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-scolds-eu-over-statement-about-south-china-sea-2024-07-12/</link><description>中国谴责欧盟就南海问题发表的声明，称后者无视这一棘手问题的历史和客观事实，并“公然支持”所谓菲律宾侵犯其主权的行为。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 02:09:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-scolds-eu-over-statement-about-south-china-sea-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾拒绝“使用武力”损害其南海利益</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-rejects-any-undermining-its-south-china-sea-interests-2024-07-12/</link><description>官员周五表示，菲律宾拒绝“使用武力”损害其在有争议的南海的利益，但不希望发生任何冲突，并已与中国就缓解有争议的浅滩的紧张局势达成一致。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 01:44:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-rejects-any-undermining-its-south-china-sea-interests-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>日元因干预紧张而波动；亚洲股市本周上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-12/</link><description>周五，日元在波动的交易中上下波动，反映出投资者在美国通胀报告低于预期后日本采取干预措施支撑日元后的不安情绪。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 01:42:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>商务部长表示中国愿意加强与沙特的贸易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-willing-strengthen-trade-with-saudi-commerce-minister-says-2024-07-12/</link><description>中国商务部长周五在一份声明中表示，中国愿与沙特加强实施发展战略，密切贸易和投资交流。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 01:33:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-willing-strengthen-trade-with-saudi-commerce-minister-says-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>日本因不当处理机密信息而对军方高层进行纪律处分</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japans-pm-promises-discipline-military-mishandling-classified-information-2024-07-12/</link><description>日本周五对 200 多名国防人员进行了纪律处分，其中包括军方高级官员和高级官僚，原因是他们处理机密材料和其他事件不当。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 01:33:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japans-pm-promises-discipline-military-mishandling-classified-information-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国电商价格战无休止，卖家入不敷出</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-relentless-e-commerce-price-war-leaves-sellers-struggling-make-ends-meet-2024-07-12/</link><description>随着销售增长放缓、价格压力上升以及购物平台与越来越激进的政策竞争以吸引越来越注重成本的客户，中国电子商务供应商正在为生存而苦苦挣扎。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 01:31:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-relentless-e-commerce-price-war-leaves-sellers-struggling-make-ends-meet-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>日本警告中国在台湾附近举行军事演习导致紧张局势加剧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-warns-rising-tension-over-chinas-military-drills-near-taiwan-2024-07-12/</link><description>日本周五警告说，中国增加军事演习可能导致与台湾的紧张局势升级，部分目的似乎是让北京军队为可能入侵这个民主治理的岛屿做好准备。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 01:17:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-warns-rising-tension-over-chinas-military-drills-near-taiwan-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国表示绝不会接受北约峰会上的“无端指责”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-says-it-will-never-accept-unfounded-accusations-nato-summit-2024-07-12/</link><description>中国外交部表示，外交部长王毅在电话中向荷兰外长表示，中国永远不会接受本周在华盛顿举行的北约峰会上针对中国的“毫无根据的指控”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 00:59:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-says-it-will-never-accept-unfounded-accusations-nato-summit-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>干预风险加剧，日元令市场紧张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/volatile-yen-keeps-currency-market-edge-2024-07-12/</link><description>日元周五走软，原因是投资者在前一交易日大幅上涨后仍感到紧张，此前数据显示美国消费者价格意外下跌，外界猜测东京已干预货币市场。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 00:43:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/volatile-yen-keeps-currency-market-edge-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>拜登表示，美国将再次与欧洲、日本合作伙伴会面，讨论增强武器能力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/biden-says-he-has-no-good-reason-talk-putin-right-now-2024-07-12/</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登周四表示，美国将再次与欧洲和日本领导人会面，讨论如何提高他们建造武器系统的能力。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 00:14:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/biden-says-he-has-no-good-reason-talk-putin-right-now-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>拜登将副总统卡马拉·哈里斯误认为特朗普</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/biden-misidentifies-vice-president-kamala-harris-trump-2024-07-11/</link><description>总统乔·拜登在周四的一场高风险新闻发布会上将副总统卡马拉·哈里斯误认为是前总统唐纳德·特朗普。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 23:47:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/biden-misidentifies-vice-president-kamala-harris-trump-2024-07-11/</guid></item></channel></rss>